" aria-hidden="true" aria-label="sprite-close" class="fill-current" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><use href="#sprite-close"></use></svg></label></div><div class="flex flex-col p-4 sm:p-8"><a aria-current="page" class="interactive interactive-md" href="/en/">Homepage</a><a class="interactive interactive-md mt-4" href="/en/contact/">Contact</a></div><div class="mx-auto mt-auto flex px-4 pb-4 sm:px-8"><a href="https://www.x.com/paulogoncalvs" aria-label="X (opens in a new window)" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank" class="icon-link"><svg role="img" aria-hidden="true" aria-label="sprite-x" class="fill-current" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><use href="#sprite-x"></use></svg></a><a href="https://www.github.com/paulogoncalvs" aria-label="GitHub (opens in a new window)" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank" class="icon-link mx-2 sm:mx-4"><svg role="img" aria-hidden="true" aria-label="sprite-github" class="fill-current" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><use href="#sprite-github"></use></svg></a><a href="https://pt.linkedin.com/in/paulogoncalvs" aria-label="LinkedIn (opens in a new window)" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank" class="icon-link"><svg role="img" aria-hidden="true" aria-label="sprite-linkedin" class="fill-current" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><use href="#sprite-linkedin"></use></svg></a></div></div></aside><main><section class="flex flex-col items-center px-6 py-20"><h1 class="op-low animate-fade-in-down text-3xl sm:text-5xl font-bold tracking-tight text-center sm:my-2" style="--delay:0.1s;">PAULO GONÇALVES</h1><h1 class="op-low animate-fade-in-down text-xl sm:text-2xl lowercase text-center" style="--delay:0.2s;">Front-End Engineer</h1><div class="flex flex-col items-center space-y-8 pt-14 sm:flex-row sm:space-y-0"><div class="op-low animate-fade-in-down shrink-0" style="--delay:0.30000000000000004s;"><img alt="portrait of Paulo Gonçalves" width="200" height="200" src="/assets/img/paulo-goncalves.DECAHKf7.webp" srcset="/assets/img/paulo-goncalves.DECAHKf7.webp 2x" loading="eager" decoding="async" fetchpriority="high" class="transition-all duration-500 ease-out opacity-100 rounded-full shadow-[inset_0_1px_0_rgba(255,255,255,0.75),0_0_9px_rgba(0,0,0,0.2),0_3px_8px_rgba(0,0,0,0.15)] bg-white/30 border border-white/20"></div><div class="op-low animate-fade-in-down max-w-xs sm:max-w-md sm:pl-14 text-sm sm:text-base" style="--delay:0.4s;"><p>Native of Vila Nova de Gaia, Porto district, Portugal.</p><p class="">Currently working as a <strong>Principal Front-End Engineer</strong> at <strong>Porto Tech Center - Jumia</strong>, where I architect and develop large-scale, high-performance web applications using modern front-end frameworks and tooling.</p></div></div><div class="op-low animate-fade-in-up " style="--delay:0.6000000000000001s;"><a class="interactive interactive-icon sm:interactive-lg interactive-md mt-14" href="/en/contact/"><svg role="img" aria-hidden="true" aria-label="sprite-mail" class="fill-current" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><use href="#sprite-mail"></use></svg>Contact me</a></div></section><section class="flex flex-col items-center border-white/80 border-t bg-white/20 px-6 py-14 pb-20 text-center shadow-black/5 shadow-xs dark:border-white/15 dark:bg-zinc-900/15"><div class="w-full max-w-xs text-left sm:max-w-xl"><h2 class="op-low animate-fade-in-down text-xl sm:text-2xl mb-12 font-bold" style="--delay:0.9s;">Professional Experience</h2><div class="op-low animate-fade-in-down relative border-l-2 border-stone-300 dark:border-white/10 ml-3 space-y-8" style="--delay:0.9s;"><div class="op-low animate-fade-in-up " style="--delay:1s;"><div class="relative pl-8"><span class="absolute top-1 -left-2.25 h-4 w-4 rounded-full border-2 border-black/20 bg-black dark:border-white/20 dark:bg-white"></span><h3 class="font-semibold text-zinc-900 dark:text-white">Principal Front-End Engineer</h3><p class="text-sm text-stone-700 dark:text-zinc-300">Jumia Porto Tech Center</p><p class="mt-1 text-stone-500 text-xs dark:text-zinc-400">Oct 2022  Present · 3 years 4 months</p></div></div><div class="op-low animate-fade-in-up " style="--delay:1.07s;"><div class="relative pl-8"><span class="absolute top-1 -left-2.25 h-4 w-4 rounded-full border-2 border-stone-300 bg-stone-100 dark:border-white/10 dark:bg-zinc-700"></span><h3 class="font-semibold text-zinc-900 dark:text-white">Engineering Manager / Lead Front-End Engineer</h3><p class="text-sm text-stone-700 dark:text-zinc-300">Jumia Porto Tech Center</p><p class="mt-1 text-stone-500 text-xs dark:text-zinc-400">Apr 2021  Sep 2022 · 1 year 6 months</p></div></div><div class="op-low animate-fade-in-up " style="--delay:1.1400000000000001s;"><div class="relative pl-8"><span class="absolute top-1 -left-2.25 h-4 w-4 rounded-full border-2 border-stone-300 bg-stone-100 dark:border-white/10 dark:bg-zinc-700"></span><h3 class="font-semibold text-zinc-900 dark:text-white">Lead Front-End Engineer</h3><p class="text-sm text-stone-700 dark:text-zinc-300">Jumia Porto Tech Center</p><p class="mt-1 text-stone-500 text-xs dark:text-zinc-400">Oct 2019  Mar 2021 · 1 year 6 months</p></div></div><div class="op-low animate-fade-in-up " style="--delay:1.21s;"><div class="relative pl-8"><span class="absolute top-1 -left-2.25 h-4 w-4 rounded-full border-2 border-stone-300 bg-stone-100 dark:border-white/10 dark:bg-zinc-700"></span><h3 class="font-semibold text-zinc-900 dark:text-white">Senior Front-End Engineer</h3><p class="text-sm text-stone-700 dark:text-zinc-300">Jumia Porto Tech Center</p><p class="mt-1 text-stone-500 text-xs dark:text-zinc-400">Apr 2018  Sep 2019 · 1 year 6 months</p></div></div><div class="op-low animate-fade-in-up " style="--delay:1.2800000000000002s;"><div class="relative pl-8"><span class="absolute top-1 -left-2.25 h-4 w-4 rounded-full border-2 border-stone-300 bg-stone-100 dark:border-white/10 dark:bg-zinc-700"></span><h3 class="font-semibold text-zinc-900 dark:text-white">Senior Front-End Developer</h3><p class="text-sm text-stone-700 dark:text-zinc-300">Rocket Internet GmbH</p><p class="mt-1 text-stone-500 text-xs dark:text-zinc-400">Jan 2017  Mar 2018 · 1 year 3 months</p></div></div><div class="op-low animate-fade-in-up " style="--delay:1.35s;"><div class="relative pl-8"><span class="absolute top-1 -left-2.25 h-4 w-4 rounded-full border-2 border-stone-300 bg-stone-100 dark:border-white/10 dark:bg-zinc-700"></span><h3 class="font-semibold text-zinc-900 dark:text-white">Advanced Developer</h3><p class="text-sm text-stone-700 dark:text-zinc-300">Rocket Internet GmbH</p><p class="mt-1 text-stone-500 text-xs dark:text-zinc-400">Mar 2016  Dec 2016 · 10 months</p></div></div><div class="op-low animate-fade-in-up " style="--delay:1.42s;"><div class="relative pl-8"><span class="absolute top-1 -left-2.25 h-4 w-4 rounded-full border-2 border-stone-300 bg-stone-100 dark:border-white/10 dark:bg-zinc-700"></span><h3 class="font-semibold text-zinc-900 dark:text-white">Multimedia Engineer</h3><p class="text-sm text-stone-700 dark:text-zinc-300">Myone - Comunicação Multimédia</p><p class="mt-1 text-stone-500 text-xs dark:text-zinc-400">Jan 2015  Feb 2016 · 1 year 2 months</p></div></div><div class="op-low animate-fade-in-up " style="--delay:1.49s;"><div class="relative pl-8"><span class="absolute top-1 -left-2.25 h-4 w-4 rounded-full border-2 border-stone-300 bg-stone-100 dark:border-white/10 dark:bg-zinc-700"></span><h3 class="font-semibold text-zinc-900 dark:text-white">Web Designer | New Media Developer</h3><p class="text-sm text-stone-700 dark:text-zinc-300">Medula - Design de Comunicação</p><p class="mt-1 text-stone-500 text-xs dark:text-zinc-400">Mar 2014  Dec 2014 · 10 months</p></div></div></div><p class="op-low animate-fade-in-down pt-12 text-sm" style="--delay:1.1s;">For more technical details and experience, please visit my <a href="https://pt.linkedin.com/in/paulogoncalvs" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank" class="underline">LinkedIn profile</a>.</p></div></section></main><footer><div class="border border-white/80 border-r-0 border-l-0 bg-white/20 p-6 text-center shadow-black/5 shadow-xs dark:border-white/15 dark:bg-zinc-900/35"><div class="flex flex-col items-center pt-10 pb-8"><p class="pb-4 font-bold text-sm">Website Technology Stack:</p><div class="flex flex-wrap justify-center align-middle"><a href="https://www.typescriptlang.org/" aria-label="TypeScript (opens in a new window)" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank" class="icon-link translate-up"><svg role="img" aria-hidden="true" aria-label="sprite-typescript" class="fill-current" width="32" height="32" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><use href="#sprite-typescript"></use></svg></a><a href="https://preactjs.com/" aria-label="Preact (opens in a new window)" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank" class="icon-link translate-up"><svg role="img" aria-hidden="true" aria-label="sprite-preact" class="fill-current" width="32" height="32" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><use href="#sprite-preact"></use></svg></a><a href="https://vite.dev/" aria-label="Vite (opens in a new window)" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank" class="icon-link translate-up"><svg role="img" aria-hidden="true" aria-label="sprite-vite" class="fill-current" width="32" height="32" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><use href="#sprite-vite"></use></svg></a><a href="https://pnpm.io/" aria-label="pnpm (opens in a new window)" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank" class="icon-link translate-up"><svg role="img" aria-hidden="true" aria-label="sprite-pnpm" class="fill-current" width="32" height="32" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><use href="#sprite-pnpm"></use></svg></a><a href="https://developers.google.com/web/tools/workbox" aria-label="Workbox (opens in a new window)" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank" class="icon-link translate-up"><svg role="img" aria-hidden="true" aria-label="sprite-workbox" class="fill-current" width="32" height="32" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><use href="#sprite-workbox"></use></svg></a><a 